547
00:29:19,767 --> 00:29:22,167
Astaga, ini dia.

548
00:29:22,167 --> 00:29:24,100
Aku harus ke toilet.

549
00:29:24,100 --> 00:29:27,833
Selagi aku di toilet,
kalian berbaikanlah sendiri.

